---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '@/lib/site';
const base = SITE.url.replace(/\/$/, '');
---
<BaseLayout title="Developer API · EduRankAI" description="REST API for universities and LMS platforms to pull the EduRankAI lab and course catalogue and embed our virtual labs.">
<style>
  body { background: #0a0a0c; color: #e8e8ee; }
  .dv { max-width: 920px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 48px 6vw 100px; }
  .dv h1 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: clamp(34px, 6vw, 56px); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 0 0 10px; }
  .dv .eyebrow { font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #67e8f9; font-weight: 700; }
  .dv .lead { font-size: 16px; color: #b8b8c4; line-height: 1.7; max-width: 640px; }
  .dv h2 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600; margin: 40px 0 8px; }
  .dv h3 { font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.06em; color: #67e8f9; margin: 26px 0 6px; }
  .dv p { color: #b8b8c4; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 14.5px; }
  .dv code.inl { background: #15151a; border: 1px solid #2a2a35; border-radius: 5px; padding: 2px 6px; font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace; font-size: 12.5px; color: #fbbf24; }
  .dv pre { background: #11131a; border: 1px solid #2a2a35; border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px; overflow-x: auto; font-size: 12.5px; color: #cfd6da; font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace; line-height: 1.7; }
  .dv .ep { display: inline-block; font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; background: #11131a; border: 1px solid #2a2a35; border-radius: 6px; padding: 5px 10px; color: #86efac; }
  .dv table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 10px; font-size: 13px; }
  .dv th, .dv td { text-align: left; padding: 8px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #1a1a1f; }
  .dv th { font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #8a8a94; }
  .dv a { color: #67e8f9; }
</style>
<main class="dv">
  <p class="eyebrow">EduRankAI · Developer API v1</p>
  <h1>Integrate our labs into your campus.</h1>
  <p class="lead">A read-only REST API for universities and LMS platforms: pull the catalogue of 36+ virtual labs and published courses, and embed any lab inside your own platform with a single signed URL — no login wall for your students.</p>

  <h2>Authentication</h2>
  <p>Every request needs an API key (issued by an EduRankAI admin under <code class="inl">Admin · API Keys</code>). Send it in the <code class="inl">x-api-key</code> header (or <code class="inl">Authorization: Bearer &lt;key&gt;</code>). Keys are read-only and can be revoked at any time.</p>
  <pre>curl -H "x-api-key: erk_live_xxxxxxxx" {base}/api/v1/labs</pre>

  <h2>Endpoints</h2>

  <h3><span class="ep">GET /api/v1/labs</span></h3>
  <p>List every embeddable virtual lab with a direct URL and a login-free <code class="inl">embed_url</code> for iframing.</p>
  <pre>{`{
  "ok": true,
  "count": 36,
  "labs": [
    {
      "slug": "vlsi",
      "name": "VLSI & Digital Design",
      "url": "${base}/aquintutor/labs/vlsi",
      "embed_url": "${base}/aquintutor/labs/vlsi?embed_token=..."
    }
  ]
}`}</pre>

  <h3><span class="ep">GET /api/v1/embed?slug=&lt;slug&gt;</span></h3>
  <p>Get a ready-to-paste iframe + signed embed URL for one lab.</p>
  <pre>{`{
  "ok": true,
  "slug": "vlsi",
  "name": "VLSI & Digital Design",
  "embed_url": "${base}/aquintutor/labs/vlsi?embed_token=...",
  "iframe": "<iframe src=\\"...\\" style=\\"width:100%;height:760px;border:0;\\" allow=\\"fullscreen\\"></iframe>"
}`}</pre>

  <h3><span class="ep">GET /api/v1/courses</span></h3>
  <p>List published courses (slug, title, category, lesson count, enrolment).</p>

  <h2>Embedding a lab in your LMS</h2>
  <p>Drop the <code class="inl">embed_url</code> into an iframe anywhere in your platform. The signed <code class="inl">embed_token</code> authorises that one lab, so your students do not need an EduRankAI login.</p>
  <pre>{`<iframe
  src="${base}/aquintutor/labs/vlsi?embed_token=..."
  style="width:100%;height:760px;border:0;"
  allow="fullscreen"></iframe>`}</pre>

  <h2>Notes</h2>
  <table>
    <tr><th>Topic</th><th>Detail</th></tr>
    <tr><td>CORS</td><td>All <code class="inl">/api/v1/*</code> endpoints are CORS-enabled for browser calls.</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Rate &amp; usage</td><td>Per-key call counts are tracked; abusive keys can be revoked.</td></tr>
    <tr><td>LTI</td><td>LTI 1.3 deep-linking is on the roadmap; today, embed via the signed iframe URL.</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Support</td><td>Contact your EduRankAI partnership manager to obtain a key.</td></tr>
  </table>
</main>
</BaseLayout>
